idewall-detail-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Tufo-Gravel-Thundero-tubeless-gravel-bike-tires_affordable-durable-mixed-surface-grip_sidewall-detail-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Tufo-Gravel-Thundero-tubeless-gravel-bike-tires_affordable-durable-mixed-surface-grip_sidewall-detail-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Tufo-Gravel-Thundero-tubeless-gravel-bike-tires_affordable-durable-mixed-surface-grip_sidewall-detail-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Tufo-Gravel-Thundero-tubeless-gravel-bike-tires_affordable-durable-mixed-surface-grip_sidewall-detail-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Tufo-Gravel-Thundero-tubeless-gravel-bike-tires_affordable-durable-mixed-surface-grip_sidewall-detail-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a></p><p>The move into gravel tires is of course a logical one. First, there’s that on-going boom of anything with the word ‘gravel’ written on the side of it.</p><p>But Tufo have also already been openly producing Donnelly’s <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/07/01/donnelly-mso-wc-brings-240tpi-cx-world-cup-level-casing-to-eu-made-gravel-tires/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">premium World Cup level</a> cross &amp; gravel tires for a few seasons – dialing in that light, durable, affordable, made-in-Europe construction.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Tufo-Gravel-tires_Gravel-Thundero-Gravel-Speedero-700x40mm-options.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Tufo-Gravel-tires_Gravel-Thundero-Gravel-Speedero-700x40mm-options.jpg\" alt=\"Tufo Gravel 